Key Match Events: Jaker Ali collided with Anamul Haque while attempting to catch Pramod Madushan off Taskin Ahmed's bowling, leading to his hospitalization.
Soumya Sarkar left the field due to a neck injury after striking an advertising board, and Mustafizur Rahman also had to leave due to cramping.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Umpire Tanvir Ahmed took over for Richard Kettleborough due to heat-related issues.
